aa(lp225
VLet me show you an example.
p226
aVHere's another project,
p227
aVand I saw this when I was visiting
p228
aVone of the computer clubhouses.
p229
aVThese are after-school learning centers that we helped start
p230
aVthat help young people from low-income communities
p231
aVlearn to express themselves creatively with new technologies.
